item.title: [PLEASE HELP!] Compiler says.... [PLEASE HELP!]
item.dc:creator: @Aftermath2k8 Aftermath2k8
item.description:
@Aftermath2k8 wrote:

Metal, Offline or Online registration?[br][br][size=1]Posted on: April 20, 2008, 08:22:17 PM[/size][hr][quote=“feaver wind, post:2, topic:201582”]go to your compiler, right click it, then go to edit.

Once your there, search for something that says jdk1.6_

You should see something like this:

jdk1.6.0_05

Change the 5 on the end to 6

Then it should look like this

jdk1.6.0_06

Hope that helped…

Doesnt work on all compilers…

=[/quote]

Errm when I right click Compiler and Edit, the coding says:

if exist “%programfiles%\Java” (call :compile “%programfiles%\Java”) else (goto error)

if defined p (goto end)

“%programfiles%\Internet Explorer\iexplore.exe” http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp
